### Payment Handles API - Devstack Test Requests
### Used for testing payment handle decomp on devstack

@devstack_label = ph-decomp
@nca_base_url = https://nca.dev.razorpay.in
@api_base_url = https://api.dev.razorpay.in
@merchant_id = LJ3P0FyFtOULha
@mode = live
# Authorization: base64("RANDOM_NCA_USER:RANDOM_NCA_PASSWORD")
@nca_auth = Basic UkFORE9NX05DQV9VU0VSOlJBTkRPTV9OQ0FfUEFTU1dPUkQ=
@dual_write_state = dual_write_no_reads_no_external
@monolith_only_state = monolith_only

###
# ============================================================
# payment_handle_create (POST /v1/payment_handle)
# ============================================================

### Create Payment Handle - monolith_only (pure proxy)
POST {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_handle
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{monolith_only_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{}

###
### Create Payment Handle - dual_write (proxy + NCA DB write)
POST {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_handle
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{dual_write_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{}

###
# ============================================================
# payment_handle_update (PATCH /v1/payment_handle)
# ============================================================

### Update Payment Handle - monolith_only (pure proxy)
PATCH {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_handle
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{monolith_only_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{
  "slug": "test-handle"
}

###
### Update Payment Handle - dual_write (proxy + NCA DB update)
PATCH {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_handle
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{dual_write_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{
  "slug": "updated-handle"
}

###
# ============================================================
# payment_page_create_order (for handle entity) 
# - Tests routing to handle vs page experiment
# ============================================================

### Create Order for Handle Page - should use handle experiment
# Replace <handle-page-id> with actual payment handle page ID (pl_xxx)
POST {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_pages/<handle-page-id>/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{monolith_only_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "INR"
}

###
### Create Order for Regular Page - should use page experiment (regression)
# Replace <page-id> with actual payment page ID
POST {{nca_base_url}}/v1/payment_pages/<page-id>/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-Razorpay-Merchant-Id: {{merchant_id}}
X-Razorpay-Mode: {{mode}}
X-Proxy-State: {{monolith_only_state}}
rzpctx-dev-serve-user: {{devstack_label}}
Authorization: {{nca_auth}}

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "currency": "INR"
}
